/**
 * Notifications Component
 *
 * The notification bell, badge, and dropdown panel are embedded directly
 * in Navbar.astro for positioning purposes. This file serves as the
 * reference for the notifications system API.
 *
 * localStorage key: "akool-notifications"
 * Each notification: { id: string, text: string, time: string, read: boolean, link: string }
 *
 * To add a notification from any script:
 *   window.__addNotification("تم الرد على تعليقك", "/articles/my-article#comments")
 *
 * Sample notifications:
 *   - "تم الرد على تعليقك"
 *   - "تمت الموافقة على مشاركتك"
 *   - "مقال جديد: عنوان المقال"
 *   - "تم حفظ مقالك في المفضلة"
 */
